latestIgtvVideos.title: This or That ft. @anour_treatyourself
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I came across @anour_treatyourself through @shoponlbb, and I’m so thankful that I discovered them! 

☕️Crunchy Cappuccino Coffee Scrub☕️
I have extremely dry body, this scrub is sooo good! It removes dead cells, gives clear skin, leaves a soft texture and SMELLS LIKE COFFEE😍

🌵Aloe Glaze Aloe Vera Gel🌵
I LOVE aloe vera gel on my skin, hair, body literally everywhere. This one is light weight, soothing, reduced any pigments/ scars and hydrates at NEXT LEVEL! 

🍇Yummy Berry Lip Scrub🍇
Exfoliating lips is damn important! I exfoliate on weekly basis. It keeps my lips soft and retains the moisture keeping cracks in check! 

🍒Cherry Bomb Lip & Cheek Tint🍒
This tint is literally BOMB! It is a versatile product, I use it on my lips, cheeks, eyes and nose too! LOVE LOVE LOVE the fragrance🥰

ENGAGE on this IGTV- to encourage & support me, you can shoot your questions too👩🏻‍💻
